snippet.title: The Walls Official Early Gameplay Trailer | DEV Unreal Engine 5 |
snippet.description:
It is a trailer video of The Walls, compiled from early in-game images and in-game clips.

The Walls is an interactive experience game in the psychological thriller and horror genre, developed with Unreal engine 5 game engine technology. It contains a narrative that drags us into tension-filled places with a realistic and dark atmosphere.

Release date: TBA

For news from developers and all new developments about the game
Subscribe to YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/@UCGFq5Wy7SX9ZXhMRFvYZJew 
Join the Discord community: https://bit.ly/thewallsdc
Follow on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thewallsgame/
